.TH LOOTSHEET-DB 1 "Mar 2026" "LootSheet" "LootSheet Manual"
.SH NAME
lootsheet-db \\- Inspect database state and run schema migrations
.SH SYNOPSIS
lootsheet db [flags]
.SH DESCRIPTION
LootSheet CLI

Usage:
  lootsheet db status
  lootsheet db migrate

Subcommands:
  status   inspect whether the configured SQLite database is uninitialized, current, upgradeable, foreign, or damaged
  migrate  apply pending embedded schema migrations to an existing LootSheet database

Examples:
  lootsheet db status
  lootsheet db migrate
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
-h, --help
help for db
.SH SEE ALSO
lootsheet(1)
lootsheet-db-migrate(1)
lootsheet-db-status(1)
